																<h1 class="post-title">10 Ways to Design Your Instagram Grid Layout Like a Pro</h1>
							</header>

							<div class="excerpt-content">
								<p>Your Instagram grid layout is your chance to show potential followers your vibe or brand at a glance. What message do you want to send?</p>
